HEADWORD: Wel-begone
<hw>Wel"-be*gone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>wel-begon</ets>. See <er>Well</er>, and <er>Begone</er>.]</ety>
<def>Surrounded with happiness or prosperity.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

